FIFO: Overwrites oldest backup first.  
GFS: Daily (Son), Weekly (Father), Monthly (Grandfather).  
Tower of Hanoi: Multi-set rotation for long-term retention.  
Media Rotation: Protects backups from loss and overwriting.

Full Backup: Copies all data every time; longest time, most storage.  
Incremental Backup: Copies changes since last backup; fastest, least storage; restore = full + incrementals.  
Differential Backup: Copies changes since last full; medium speed/storage; restore = full + latest differential.
